# Backend Authentication & Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)

This is a backend service built using **Node.js**, **Express**, and **MongoDB**.
The project provides a secure authentication system with **Signup**, **Login**, and **Role-based access control (Admin/User)**. 
Middlewares are used to protect routes based on user roles and ensure secure API communication.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

* User Signup & Login
* Password hashing for security
* JWT-based authentication
* Role-based authorization (User/Admin)
* Structured and scalable project architecture

---

## ğŸ§± Tech Stack

* **Node.js**
* **Express.js**
